title: NFL ATL: Free agency winners and losers
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Free agency winners and losers
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler -- breaks down which teams performed best and worst in free agency and, as always, picks apart the latest headlines from around the NFL.
